t: Emily Current & Meritt Elliott | The Wall Group
s: May 3, 2024 - Emily Current and Meritt Elliott are a Los Angeles-based stylist and designer duo. Together they created premium denim label Current/Elliott in 2008, and exited the brand in a private equity buyout in 2012. In Spring 2015, they launched a new women’s line, The Great.

s: We regret that due to technical challenges caused by new regulations in Europe, we can for the time being no longer accept orders from the European Union. If you reside in the UK you can continue to order from our UK websites or shop from our locations and partners.

t: Emily Current and Meritt Elliott Are Designing Again, On Their Own Terms - Fashionista
s: March 13, 2015 - Emily Current and Meritt Elliott are leaving their eponymous label. According to WWD, Current and Elliott didn't offer any explanation as to why they'd decided to leave their label. But there were some hints over the past few years that all was not well between the designers and the Current/Elliott brand...
